{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://github.com/mcp-tool-shop-org/backprop-trace/schemas/receipt.v0.6.0.json",
  "title": "backprop-trace canonical receipt schema v0.6.0",
  "description": "v0.9.2 classical PyTorch-style SGD momentum extension. FORCED bump over receipt.v0.5.0 because Update.optimizer.name was a closed enum ['sgd', 'adam', 'adamw'] and AdamState had additionalProperties:false on required keys [m, v] — adding 'sgd_momentum' as a new optimizer with a distinct state shape ({buffer} instead of {m, v}) could not happen in-place. v0.5.0 SGD/Adam/AdamW receipts continue to validate against v0.5.0 schema unchanged (byte-equal preservation for v0.1-v0.9.1 fixture lineage); v0.9.2 sgd_momentum receipts declare schema_version: '0.6.0'. Rule 21 (classical PyTorch-style SGD momentum recurrence) fires on this version. NO Nesterov (reserved with nesterov: const false — v0.9.3 widens to boolean). NO dampening (reserved with dampening: const 0 — v0.9.3 widens to number). NO SGD coupled L2 weight decay (rejected at engine boundary with 'deferred to v0.10' message; v0.10 adds the Rules 6/7 coupled-L2 branch). NO AMSGrad / NAdam / RAdam / Lion / per-parameter-groups / LR schedules / gradient clipping / mixed precision (deferred to v0.10+). Trust framing: Rule 21 is a STRUCTURAL CONSISTENCY check (does the recorded buffer recurrence and parameter update match the classical PyTorch-style equations?), NOT a producer-authenticity check. An attacker who controls every byte of the sidecar and recomputes a consistent (g, buffer, update) triple passes Rule 21 trivially — analogous to the Rule 17 bundle-integrity caveat, the Rule 22-24 Adam-rule caveat from v0.9.1, and the Fang et al. 2023 EuroS&P spoofing class against Proof-of-Learning. For producer-identity binding, combine with Rule 16 (attestor.signed_subject_digest), Sigstore / cosign signature, or out-of-band attestation.",
  "type": "object",
  "x-changes-from-v0.5.0": [
    "schema_version const bumped 0.5.0 -> 0.6.0",
    "Update.optimizer.name enum widened: ['sgd', 'adam', 'adamw'] -> ['sgd', 'adam', 'adamw', 'sgd_momentum']. v0.5.0 receipts use the narrower enum unchanged.",
    "OptimizerConfig.name enum widened: same widening.",
    "NEW $defs/MomentumState block: { buffer: number }, additionalProperties: false, required: ['buffer']. Classical PyTorch-style SGD momentum state — single per-parameter scalar tracking the accumulated velocity buffer (PyTorch's state['momentum_buffer'] one-token form). Distinct from AdamState's (m, v) pair.",
    "Update.optimizer.state_before / state_after typed as oneOf [AdamState, MomentumState] at the schema layer. Reconciler Rule 20 enforces that the actual shape matches optimizer.name (Adam/AdamW receipts get AdamState; sgd_momentum receipts get MomentumState) — schema validates either; reconciler strict-checks.",
    "OptimizerConfig gains OPTIONAL momentum: number (0, 1). Conditionally REQUIRED when optimizer_config.name === 'sgd_momentum' via new allOf if/then clause.",
    "OptimizerConfig gains RESERVED nesterov: { const: false } (optional; v0.9.3 widens to boolean for Nesterov accelerated gradient — see https://arxiv.org/abs/1412.6980 / Sutskever et al. 2013 ICML for the lookahead update form). When present in v0.9.2, MUST be literally false. When absent, treated as false. Nesterov is NOT supported in v0.9.2 — schema rejects nesterov: true with a clear schema-level error; engine rejects sidecars that bypass schema validation.",
    "OptimizerConfig gains RESERVED dampening: { const: 0 } (optional; v0.9.3 widens to number in [0, 1) for PyTorch's torch.optim.SGD(dampening=tau) recurrence buffer_t = mu * buffer_{t-1} + (1 - tau) * gradient). When present in v0.9.2, MUST be literally 0. When absent, treated as 0. Dampening is NOT supported in v0.9.2 — schema rejects dampening != 0.",
    "OptimizerConfig gains conditional NOT clause: when optimizer_config.name === 'sgd_momentum', weight_decay MUST be absent (SGD coupled L2 weight decay is deferred to v0.10 — needs Rules 6/7 third branch distinct from AdamW's decoupled). Schema enforces absence via if/then 'not required weight_decay' clause.",
    "NO removed fields. NO renamed fields. NO breaking changes to existing v0.5.0 SGD/Adam/AdamW receipt shape. v0.5.0 receipts validate against v0.5.0 schema unchanged. v0.9.2 sgd_momentum receipts declare schema_version: '0.6.0' and pick up the new conditional requirements."
  ],
  "x-order": [
    "schema_version",
    "fixture",
    "step",
    "fixture_status",
    "source_framework",
    "attestor",
    "metadata",
    "numeric_policy",
    "bias_policy",
    "topology",
    "learning_rate",
    "optimizer_config",
    "trace_id",
    "step_index",
    "batch",
    "inputs",
    "targets",
    "parameters_before",
    "per_sample",
    "forward",
    "loss",
    "backward",
    "updates",
    "parameters_after",
    "post_update_forward",
    "post_update_loss"
  ],
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "required": [
    "schema_version",
    "fixture",
    "step",
    "fixture_status",
    "numeric_policy",
    "bias_policy",
    "topology",
    "learning_rate",
    "inputs",
    "targets",
    "parameters_before",
    "forward",
    "loss",
    "backward",
    "updates",
    "parameters_after"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "schema_version": { "const": "0.6.0" },
    "fixture": { "type": "string" },
    "step": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1 },
    "fixture_status": { "$ref": "#/$defs/FixtureStatus" },
    "source_framework": { "$ref": "#/$defs/SourceFramework" },
    "attestor": { "$ref": "#/$defs/Attestor" },
    "metadata": { "type": "object" },
    "numeric_policy": { "$ref": "#/$defs/NumericPolicy" },
    "bias_policy": { "$ref": "#/$defs/BiasPolicy" },
    "topology": { "$ref": "#/$defs/Topology" },
    "learning_rate": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
    "optimizer_config": {
      "description": "OPTIONAL. REQUIRED at the reconciler boundary when any update.optimizer.name is in {adam, adamw, sgd_momentum}. SGD-only receipts MAY omit this block. When present, declares global optimizer hyperparameters. Rules 20, 22, 23, 24, 25, 26 (Adam-family) and Rule 21 (sgd_momentum) consume these values. v0.9.2 supports sgd / adam / adamw / sgd_momentum only.",
      "$ref": "#/$defs/OptimizerConfig"
    },
    "trace_id": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[0-9a-f]{32}$" },
    "step_index": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 0 },
    "batch": { "$ref": "#/$defs/Batch" },
    "inputs": { "$ref": "#/$defs/UnitNumberMap" },
    "targets": { "$ref": "#/$defs/UnitNumberMap" },
    "parameters_before": { "$ref": "#/$defs/ParameterMap" },
    "per_sample": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": {
        "type": "object",
        "additionalProperties": false,
        "required": ["inputs", "targets", "forward", "loss"],
        "properties": {
          "inputs": { "$ref": "#/$defs/UnitNumberMap" },
          "targets": { "$ref": "#/$defs/UnitNumberMap" },
          "forward": { "$ref": "#/$defs/ForwardMap" },
          "loss": { "$ref": "#/$defs/Loss" }
        }
      }
    },
    "forward": { "$ref": "#/$defs/ForwardMap" },
    "loss": { "$ref": "#/$defs/Loss" },
    "backward": { "$ref": "#/$defs/Backward" },
    "updates": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "items": { "$ref": "#/$defs/Update" }
    },
    "parameters_after": { "$ref": "#/$defs/ParameterMap" },
    "post_update_forward": { "$ref": "#/$defs/PostUpdateForward" },
    "post_update_loss": { "$ref": "#/$defs/PostUpdateLoss" }
  },
  "allOf": [
    {
      "x-purpose": "Co-presence guard: trace_id and step_index. Same as v0.4.0/v0.5.0.",
      "anyOf": [
        { "not": { "required": ["step_index"] } },
        { "required": ["trace_id"] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "x-purpose": "Co-presence guard inverse: trace_id requires step_index. Same as v0.4.0/v0.5.0.",
      "anyOf": [
        { "not": { "required": ["trace_id"] } },
        { "required": ["step_index"] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "x-purpose": "v0.5.0 carried forward: when optimizer_config.name is adam or adamw, beta1/beta2/epsilon/t are required.",
      "type": "object",
      "if": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["optimizer_config"],
        "properties": {
          "optimizer_config": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["name"],
            "properties": { "name": { "enum": ["adam", "adamw"] } }
          }
        }
      },
      "then": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "optimizer_config": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["name", "learning_rate", "beta1", "beta2", "epsilon", "t"]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "x-purpose": "v0.5.0 carried forward: when optimizer_config.name is adamw, weight_decay is also required.",
      "type": "object",
      "if": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["optimizer_config"],
        "properties": {
          "optimizer_config": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["name"],
            "properties": { "name": { "const": "adamw" } }
          }
        }
      },
      "then": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "optimizer_config": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["name", "learning_rate", "beta1", "beta2", "epsilon", "t", "weight_decay"]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "x-purpose": "v0.9.2 NEW: when optimizer_config.name is sgd_momentum, momentum hyperparameter is required.",
      "type": "object",
      "if": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["optimizer_config"],
        "properties": {
          "optimizer_config": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["name"],
            "properties": { "name": { "const": "sgd_momentum" } }
          }
        }
      },
      "then": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "optimizer_config": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["name", "learning_rate", "momentum"]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "x-purpose": "v0.9.2 NEW: when optimizer_config.name is sgd_momentum, weight_decay MUST be absent (SGD coupled L2 deferred to v0.10).",
      "type": "object",
      "if": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["optimizer_config"],
        "properties": {
          "optimizer_config": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["name"],
            "properties": { "name": { "const": "sgd_momentum" } }
          }
        }
      },
      "then": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "optimizer_config": {
            "type": "object",
            "not": { "required": ["weight_decay"] }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "$defs": {
    "UnitOrder": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["input", "hidden", "output"],
      "properties": {
        "input": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" } },
        "hidden": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" } },
        "output": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" } }
      }
    },
    "ParameterOrder": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "uniqueItems": true,
      "items": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" }
    },
    "FixtureStatus": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["authoring_state", "verification_state", "canonical", "promote_to", "describes_in", "blockers_to_promotion"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["authoring_state", "verification_state", "canonical"],
      "properties": {
        "authoring_state": {
          "enum": ["hand_derived", "engine_generated", "engine_generated_general", "deliberately_corrupted", "external_imported"]
        },
        "verification_state": {
          "enum": ["pending_engine_reproduction", "engine_reproduced_byte_equal", "expected_to_fail_reconciliation", "engine_recompute_matched_within_tolerance", "engine_recompute_disagreed", "engine_recompute_skipped_with_basis"]
        },
        "canonical": { "type": "boolean" },
        "promote_to": { "type": "string" },
        "describes_in": { "type": "string" },
        "blockers_to_promotion": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } }
      }
    },
    "SourceFramework": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["name", "version", "information_uri", "extractor"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["name", "version"],
      "properties": {
        "name": { "enum": ["pytorch", "jax", "tensorflow", "hand_derived", "backprop_trace_engine"] },
        "version": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 },
        "information_uri": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 },
        "extractor": {
          "type": "object",
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "required": ["name", "version"],
          "properties": {
            "name": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 },
            "version": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Attestor": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["computed_by", "verified_by", "differential_tolerance", "import_provenance", "skip_basis", "signed_subject_digest", "bundle_root_digest"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["computed_by", "verified_by", "differential_tolerance"],
      "properties": {
        "computed_by": { "$ref": "#/$defs/AttestorIdentity" },
        "verified_by": { "$ref": "#/$defs/AttestorIdentity" },
        "differential_tolerance": {
          "type": "object",
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "required": ["atol", "rtol"],
          "properties": {
            "atol": { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 },
            "rtol": { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 }
          }
        },
        "import_provenance": {
          "type": "object",
          "x-order": ["source_format", "source_hash", "import_timestamp"],
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "required": ["source_format", "source_hash"],
          "properties": {
            "source_format": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 },
            "source_hash": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^sha256:[0-9a-f]{64}$" },
            "import_timestamp": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 }
          }
        },
        "skip_basis": {
          "enum": ["hardware_nondeterminism", "framework_op_unsupported", "distributed_only_field", "attested_third_party"]
        },
        "signed_subject_digest": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^sha256:[0-9a-f]{64}$" },
        "bundle_root_digest": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^sha256:[0-9a-f]{64}$" }
      }
    },
    "AttestorIdentity": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["kind", "identity"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["kind", "identity"],
      "properties": {
        "kind": { "enum": ["framework", "engine", "hand_derivation"] },
        "identity": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 }
      }
    },
    "OptimizerConfig": {
      "description": "v0.9.2 — global optimizer hyperparameters. SGD: name + learning_rate. Adam/AdamW: + beta1, beta2, epsilon, t, weight_decay (adamw only). sgd_momentum: + momentum (required, in (0, 1)); reserved fields nesterov (const false) and dampening (const 0) for v0.9.3 forward-compat. weight_decay on sgd_momentum is rejected at schema level (allOf conditional) — SGD coupled L2 deferred to v0.10. Closed-shape additionalProperties:false preserved.",
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["name", "learning_rate", "beta1", "beta2", "epsilon", "weight_decay", "t", "momentum", "nesterov", "dampening"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["name", "learning_rate"],
      "properties": {
        "name": { "enum": ["sgd", "adam", "adamw", "sgd_momentum"] },
        "learning_rate": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
        "beta1": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0, "exclusiveMaximum": 1 },
        "beta2": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0, "exclusiveMaximum": 1 },
        "epsilon": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
        "weight_decay": { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 },
        "t": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1 },
        "momentum": {
          "description": "v0.9.2 — momentum coefficient mu for classical PyTorch-style SGD momentum (buffer_t = mu * buffer_{t-1} + gradient). Required when name === 'sgd_momentum'. Typically 0.9 in production (timm / Wilson et al. 2017 / Sutskever et al. 2013).",
          "type": "number",
          "exclusiveMinimum": 0,
          "exclusiveMaximum": 1
        },
        "nesterov": {
          "description": "v0.9.2 — RESERVED. Nesterov accelerated gradient deferred to v0.9.3 — when shipped, this widens to boolean. In v0.9.2, MUST be literally false when present (schema-enforced via const). When absent, treated as false (classical momentum). Sutskever et al. 2013 ICML / Nesterov 1983 for the lookahead form.",
          "const": false
        },
        "dampening": {
          "description": "v0.9.2 — RESERVED. PyTorch's torch.optim.SGD(dampening=tau) recurrence buffer_t = mu * buffer_{t-1} + (1 - tau) * gradient deferred to v0.9.3 — when shipped, this widens to number in [0, 1). In v0.9.2, MUST be literally 0 when present (schema-enforced via const). When absent, treated as 0.",
          "const": 0
        }
      }
    },
    "AdamState": {
      "description": "v0.9.1 — per-parameter Adam/AdamW state (m, v). Canonical names match Kingma & Ba 2014 Algorithm 1.",
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["m", "v"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["m", "v"],
      "properties": {
        "m": { "type": "number" },
        "v": { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 }
      }
    },
    "MomentumState": {
      "description": "v0.9.2 — per-parameter classical PyTorch-style SGD momentum state. Single scalar 'buffer' tracking the accumulated velocity (PyTorch's state['momentum_buffer'] one-token form). Distinct from AdamState's (m, v) pair. Buffer is signed (tracks gradient sign in descent direction; can be negative when accumulated descent gradient overshoots).",
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["buffer"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["buffer"],
      "properties": {
        "buffer": { "type": "number" }
      }
    },
    "OptimizerState": {
      "description": "v0.9.2 — discriminated union of per-parameter optimizer state shapes. Adam/AdamW use AdamState ({m, v}); sgd_momentum uses MomentumState ({buffer}). Schema validates that the value matches ONE of the two shapes; reconciler Rule 20 enforces that the shape matches optimizer.name (Adam/AdamW receipts get AdamState; sgd_momentum receipts get MomentumState).",
      "oneOf": [
        { "$ref": "#/$defs/AdamState" },
        { "$ref": "#/$defs/MomentumState" }
      ]
    },
    "NumericPolicy": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["number_encoding", "precision_significant_digits", "rounding", "tolerance", "computation_order", "byte_output"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["number_encoding", "precision_significant_digits", "rounding", "tolerance"],
      "properties": {
        "number_encoding": { "const": "decimal" },
        "precision_significant_digits": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1 },
        "rounding": { "const": "round_half_to_even" },
        "tolerance": {
          "oneOf": [
            {
              "type": "object", "required": ["atol", "rtol"], "additionalProperties": false,
              "properties": { "atol": { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 }, "rtol": { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 } }
            },
            { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 }
          ]
        },
        "computation_order": { "const": "schema_defined" },
        "byte_output": {
          "type": "object",
          "x-order": ["format", "json_key_order", "trailing_zero_policy", "indent"],
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "properties": {
            "format": { "const": "jsonl" },
            "json_key_order": { "const": "schema_defined" },
            "trailing_zero_policy": { "const": "pad_to_significant_digits" },
            "indent": { "const": "none" }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "BiasPolicy": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["mode", "reason", "updated_in_step", "reconciliation"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["mode", "updated_in_step"],
      "properties": {
        "mode": { "enum": ["constant", "sgd"] },
        "reason": { "type": "string" },
        "updated_in_step": { "type": "boolean" },
        "reconciliation": { "type": "string" }
      }
    },
    "Topology": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["layers", "input_size", "hidden_size", "output_size", "unit_order", "parameter_order", "parameters", "activation_hidden", "activation_output", "loss", "bias_sharing"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["layers", "input_size", "hidden_size", "output_size", "unit_order", "parameter_order", "parameters", "activation_hidden", "activation_output", "loss", "bias_sharing"],
      "properties": {
        "layers": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } },
        "input_size": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 64 },
        "hidden_size": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 64 },
        "output_size": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 64 },
        "unit_order": { "$ref": "#/$defs/UnitOrder" },
        "parameter_order": { "$ref": "#/$defs/ParameterOrder" },
        "parameters": {
          "type": "array",
          "minItems": 1,
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["id", "role"],
            "properties": {
              "id": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" },
              "role": { "enum": ["input_to_hidden_weight", "hidden_to_output_weight", "hidden_bias", "output_bias"] },
              "from_unit": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" },
              "to_unit": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" },
              "applies_to_units": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" } }
            }
          }
        },
        "activation_hidden": { "enum": ["sigmoid", "identity", "relu"] },
        "activation_output": { "enum": ["sigmoid", "identity", "relu", "softmax"] },
        "loss": { "enum": ["half_squared_error", "cross_entropy_softmax"] },
        "bias_sharing": { "enum": ["per_layer", "per_neuron"] }
      }
    },
    "UnitNumberMap": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "type": "number" } },
    "ParameterMap": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "type": "number" } },
    "ForwardMap": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/$defs/ForwardUnit" } },
    "ForwardUnit": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["net", "out"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["net", "out"],
      "properties": { "net": { "type": "number" }, "out": { "type": "number" } }
    },
    "Batch": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["size", "sample_order", "reduction"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["size", "sample_order", "reduction"],
      "properties": {
        "size": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1 },
        "sample_order": {
          "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "uniqueItems": true,
          "items": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" }
        },
        "reduction": { "enum": ["mean", "sum", "none"] }
      }
    },
    "Loss": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["per_output", "per_sample", "reduction", "total"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["per_output", "total"],
      "properties": {
        "per_output": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "type": "number" } },
        "per_sample": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "type": "number" } },
        "reduction": { "enum": ["mean", "sum", "none"] },
        "total": { "type": "number" }
      }
    },
    "Backward": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["output_error_signals", "hidden_error_signals"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["output_error_signals", "hidden_error_signals"],
      "properties": {
        "output_error_signals": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/$defs/OutputErrorSignal" } },
        "hidden_error_signals": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/$defs/HiddenErrorSignal" } }
      }
    },
    "OutputErrorSignal": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["factors", "product_order", "signal_value", "dual_form"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["factors", "product_order", "signal_value"],
      "properties": {
        "factors": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "$ref": "#/$defs/NamedFactor" } },
        "product_order": { "const": "left_to_right" },
        "signal_value": { "type": "number" },
        "dual_form": { "$ref": "#/$defs/DualForm" }
      }
    },
    "DualForm": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["jacobian_terms", "product_order", "summation_order", "summed_value"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["jacobian_terms", "product_order", "summation_order", "summed_value"],
      "properties": {
        "jacobian_terms": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "$ref": "#/$defs/JacobianTerm" } },
        "product_order": { "const": "left_to_right" },
        "summation_order": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "type": "string" } },
        "summed_value": { "type": "number" }
      }
    },
    "JacobianTerm": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["target_unit", "factors", "term_value"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["target_unit", "factors", "term_value"],
      "properties": {
        "target_unit": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$" },
        "factors": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "$ref": "#/$defs/NamedFactor" } },
        "term_value": { "type": "number" }
      }
    },
    "HiddenErrorSignal": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["downstream_contributions", "summation_order", "backpropagated_sum", "activation_derivative", "product_order", "signal_value"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["downstream_contributions", "summation_order", "backpropagated_sum", "activation_derivative", "product_order", "signal_value"],
      "properties": {
        "downstream_contributions": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "$ref": "#/$defs/DownstreamContribution" } },
        "summation_order": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "type": "string" } },
        "backpropagated_sum": { "type": "number" },
        "activation_derivative": { "type": "number" },
        "product_order": { "const": "left_to_right" },
        "signal_value": { "type": "number" }
      }
    },
    "DownstreamContribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["from", "downstream_signal", "via_weight", "weight_value", "value"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["from", "downstream_signal", "via_weight", "weight_value", "value"],
      "properties": {
        "from": { "type": "string" },
        "downstream_signal": { "type": "number" },
        "via_weight": { "type": "string" },
        "weight_value": { "type": "number" },
        "value": { "type": "number" }
      }
    },
    "NamedFactor": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["name", "from", "value"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["name", "value"],
      "properties": {
        "name": { "type": "string" },
        "from": { "type": "string" },
        "value": { "type": "number" }
      }
    },
    "Update": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["parameter_id", "kind", "layer_edge", "parameter_role", "from_unit", "to_unit", "weight_before", "optimizer", "gradient", "update", "weight_after"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["parameter_id", "kind", "weight_before", "optimizer", "gradient", "update", "weight_after"],
      "properties": {
        "parameter_id": { "type": "string" },
        "kind": { "enum": ["weight", "bias"] },
        "layer_edge": { "enum": ["input_to_hidden", "hidden_to_output", "bias_to_layer"] },
        "parameter_role": { "type": "string" },
        "from_unit": { "type": "string" },
        "to_unit": { "type": "string" },
        "weight_before": { "type": "number" },
        "optimizer": {
          "type": "object",
          "x-order": ["name", "learning_rate", "factors", "product_order", "state_before", "state_after"],
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "required": ["name", "learning_rate", "factors", "product_order"],
          "properties": {
            "name": { "enum": ["sgd", "adam", "adamw", "sgd_momentum"] },
            "learning_rate": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
            "factors": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "$ref": "#/$defs/NamedFactor" } },
            "product_order": { "const": "left_to_right" },
            "state_before": { "$ref": "#/$defs/OptimizerState" },
            "state_after": { "$ref": "#/$defs/OptimizerState" }
          }
        },
        "gradient": { "type": "number" },
        "update": { "type": "number" },
        "weight_after": { "type": "number" }
      },
      "allOf": [
        {
          "x-purpose": "v0.5.0 carried forward: per-update state required for Adam/AdamW.",
          "type": "object",
          "if": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["optimizer"],
            "properties": {
              "optimizer": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["name"],
                "properties": { "name": { "enum": ["adam", "adamw"] } }
              }
            }
          },
          "then": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "optimizer": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["name", "learning_rate", "factors", "product_order", "state_before", "state_after"]
              }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "x-purpose": "v0.9.2 NEW: per-update state required for sgd_momentum (buffer_before + buffer_after).",
          "type": "object",
          "if": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["optimizer"],
            "properties": {
              "optimizer": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["name"],
                "properties": { "name": { "const": "sgd_momentum" } }
              }
            }
          },
          "then": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "optimizer": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["name", "learning_rate", "factors", "product_order", "state_before", "state_after"]
              }
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "PostUpdateForward": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["status"],
      "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/$defs/ForwardUnit" },
      "properties": {
        "status": { "enum": ["pending_engine_first_run", "filled"] },
        "required_before_promotion": { "type": "boolean" },
        "fields_required": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } },
        "fill_specification": { "type": "string" },
        "note": { "type": "string" }
      }
    },
    "PostUpdateLoss": {
      "type": "object",
      "x-order": ["status", "required_before_promotion", "fields_required", "drift_check_against_published", "note", "per_output", "total"],
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["status"],
      "properties": {
        "status": { "enum": ["pending_engine_first_run", "filled"] },
        "required_before_promotion": { "type": "boolean" },
        "fields_required": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } },
        "drift_check_against_published": { "type": "object" },
        "note": { "type": "string" },
        "per_output": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": { "type": "number" } },
        "total": { "type": "number" }
      }
    }
  }
}
